complicated you can also do that.

7
00:00:18.350 --> 00:00:22.603
Okay, so
we've got aria-labelledby="title" and

8
00:00:22.603 --> 00:00:28.310
then the first element beneath encased
inside that SVG has to be the title.

9
00:00:28.310 --> 00:00:31.451
You can't put something else in
there first, like defs maybe or

10
00:00:31.451 --> 00:00:33.670
