monkey pants, dancing tango monkey pants.

13
00:00:42.200 --> 00:00:47.510
These have to be the same association and
only one per page too.

14
00:00:47.510 --> 00:00:53.970
So we have ID, we have a role, which is
presentation, we can also say role image.

15
00:00:53.970 --> 00:00:57.449
The reason why you have the role on
there is because you're trying to tell

16
00:00:57.449 --> 00:01:00.370
the screen reader don't read
out everything in the SVG DOM.

17
00:01:00.370 --> 00:01:05.016
So you can imagine if you were using
a screen reader to navigate a website how

18
00:01:05.016 --> 00:01:10.205
having it read it has the possibility for
all of these great accessibility things.

19
00:01:10.205 --> 00:01:11.880
Because it has a [INAUDIBLE].

20
