shape [LAUGH] to someone with a screen

21
00:01:15.499 --> 00:01:17.690
reader either, that doesn't sound great.

22
00:01:17.690 --> 00:01:22.360
So making sure it has role presentation or
role image is really important.

23
00:01:22.360 --> 00:01:25.626
Then within the title we have
to have the title in the ID,

24
00:01:25.626 --> 00:01:28.350
actually Jaws won't pick
it up without that.

25
00:01:28.350 --> 00:01:33.153
So if you leave the ID off you're,
basically, not even including a title,

26
00:01:33.153 --> 00:01:34.290
unfortunately.

